Name: AIRCRAFT SPEED IN KILOMETRES PER HOUR
AVERAGE SPEED IN KILOMETRES PER HOUR, AUTOBAHNEN FREEWAYS
Explanation: GIVES THE AVERAGE SPEED IN KILOMETRES PER HOUR OF A VEHICLE MARCHING IN A COLUMN TO BE MAINTAINED ON AUTOBAHNEN OR FREEWAYS.

Name: AVERAGE SPEED IN KILOMETRES PER HOUR, OTHER ROADS
Explanation: GIVES THE AVERAGE SPEED IN KILOMETRES PER HOUR OF A VEHICLE MARCHING IN A COLUMN TO BE MAINTAINED ON ROADS OTHER THAN AUTOBAHNEN OR FREEWAYS.
